148
00:18:33.831 --> 00:18:34.832
It's your husband.

149
00:18:37.418 --> 00:18:38.503
My husband?

150
00:18:39.545 --> 00:18:40.588
{\i1}Hello?{\i0}

151
00:18:41.172 --> 00:18:42.173
{\i1}Seyun.{\i0}

152
00:18:43.591 --> 00:18:44.592
Seyun?

153
00:18:48.137 --> 00:18:49.222
